  "title": "fix(url-sync): let the user go back in history (fix #2171)",
  "body": "To test that the behaviour is fixed, go to the [staging website](http://unhealthy-direction.surge.sh/).\r\n\r\nScenario:\r\n - select slowly three brands in the brand refinement list\r\n - go back once --> goes back right away\r\n - go back again --> goes a step back (can move forward from there)\r\n\r\nThis cannot be reproduced there: https://demo.algolia.com/instant-search-demo/",
